    "message": "fix(ci): make yaml import type-check environment-independent\n\nMove the optional pyyaml import suppression from an inline type:ignore to a\nper-module mypy override. The inline ignore was flagged as unused under strict\nmode when --ignore-missing-imports already suppressed the missing import (CI),\nwhile removing it broke type-check when pyyaml is installed without stubs. The\noverride yields identical results regardless of whether pyyaml is present.",
